occurrenceremarks: Annual, sparsely to densely pubescent, herb with linear to linear-lanceolate leaves 1-15 cm long and 0.1-0.7 cm wide. Leaves lack a distant petiole, possess margins that are entire, and have 3 distinct veins located on their underside. Plants can reach up to 21 cm in height and are characterized by a villous spike inflorescence 1-13 cm long with perfect flowers, obovate sepals, and 4 stamens, Fruits are capsules that break at or slightly below the middle and contain two approximately 2.2 mm x 1.2 mm light-dark brown seeds.

fieldnotes: Palms with trunks 6-10 m tall grouped by two or three. Trunks branched once near 5 m above ground or sometimes unbranched or two-times branched. Diameter at breast height 12-15 cm. Piassava is in a tuft among leaf sheaths, sometimes persisting around trunk for some or all of its length. Leaf sheath 88 cm long with piassava growing off of sheath, interlaced with piassava of neighboring sheaths. Petiole 96 cm long. Leaf rachis 281 cm long with 47-52 evenly spaced leaflets per side. Mature infructescence 165 cm long from where cut off where came away from trunk, three orders of branching. Mature fruit green. Parts of inflorescence at various stages of development taken from neighboring trees ; also three orders of branching. Collection: leaf tip, leaf mid section, top of petiole, leaf sheath, infructescence, inflorescence, spathe (?)

(aff. griseus), name changed per dr. ted anderson, march 1993.

occurrenceremarks: 3 herbarium sheets accessioned with same #; Sheet III/III with DES00050451 & DES00064267; Planta con tronco de 7.5 m de alto, 113 cm de diametro y 35 cm de ancho. Hojas verde-oscuro, erectas, las secas cubriendo casi todo el tallo, la parte basal de 1.4 m sin hojas, corteza fisurqda, con las marcas de las hojas impresas, base engrosada. Roseta de 3 m de alto y 3.5 m de diametro. Inflorescencia piramidal-romboidal de 7.5 m de alto (pedunculo de 1.7 m), verde, con approx. 70 ramas primarias de 1-1.7 m, las centrales son las mas grdes. Flores con ovario verde, y tepalos blanquecinos. Una rama 1 a. con 27 ramas secundarias con 55 fls. Con un total de approx. 3500 fls. En la infl. Lo prensado corresponde a una sola rama completa.
